OL,4,Ckilled in car crash hours after giving
OL,5,Cbirth
OL,7,FA woman who was forced to identify her
OL,8,Fparents just hours after giving birth
OL,9,Fhas spoken of her "heartbreak"
OL,10,Ffollowing the conviction of the man
OL,11,Fwho caused their deaths in Rutland.
OL,13,FSimarjeet Singh, 35, has been found
OL,14,Fguilty of causing the deaths of Gail
OL,15,FGale, 58, and Ian Gale, 64, by
OL,16,Fcareless driving as well as two counts
OL,17,Fof causing death by driving while
OL,18,Funinsured and two counts of causing
OL,19,Fdeath while driving without a licence.
