OL,7,FThe married couple were killed in a
OL,8,Fcar crash on the A47 Leicester Road,
OL,9,Fnear Belton in Rutland, on Friday 18
OL,10,FNovember 2022.
OL,12,FSingh had been driving a Citroen C4
OL,13,FPicasso when a witness reported seeing
OL,14,Fhim swerve and then turn into the path
OL,15,Fof oncoming traffic.
OL,17,FHe crashed head-on with a Hyundai i10
OL,18,Fbeing driven by Mrs Gale. Mr Gale was
OL,19,Fsat in the passenger seat.
