OL,5,Cbirth
OL,7,FThe pair were pronounced dead at the
OL,8,Fscene, whilst Singh sustained minor
OL,9,Finjuries.
OL,11,FLeicestershire Police found that Singh
OL,12,Fdid not have a full driving licence or
OL,13,Fvalid insurance at the time of the
OL,14,Fcollision.
OL,16,FForensic examination found that the
OL,17,Fswerve carried out by Singh was
OL,18,Findicative of being due to loss of
OL,19,Fconcentration or distraction of the
OL,20,Fdriver. Neither driver was travelling
OL,21,Fat excess speed.
