OL,7,FSingh had reported that there had been
OL,8,Fa stone or animal in the road, but no
OL,9,Fevidence of a bump, stone or animal
OL,10,Fwas found in the road or grass verges.
OL,12,FHe was found guilty at Leicester Crown
OL,13,FCourt. He has been released on bail
OL,14,Fwith conditions and is due to be
OL,15,Fsentenced on Friday 17 January.
