OL,7,FSpeaking following the conviction, Mrs
OL,8,FGale's daughter Emma Johnson, 34,
OL,9,Fsaid: "When I found out about mum's
OL,10,Fdeath I was shocked and stressed. I
OL,11,Fwas due to give birth imminently and
OL,12,Fthe stress could potentially have been
OL,13,Fdetrimental to my baby's health.
OL,15,F"Imagine then having to identity your
OL,16,Fparents bodies hours after giving
OL,17,Fbirth to your child; mum's grandchild;
OL,18,Fthe grandchild she would never meet.
OL,19,FThat is what I had to do.
